.SH "EXAMPLES"
There are three modes in which the interpreter is used: batch, interactive, or command mode\.
.
.P
In batch mode, just supply the top module with a \fBmain\fR combinator\.
.
.IP "" 4
.
.nf

$ egel helloworld\.eg
Hello world!
.
.fi
.
.IP "" 0
